metadata.name: Priest's-Calligraphy calligraphy paper
metadata.description:
Burning two pieces of blank paper produces random calligraphy characters. Please enjoy the randomly appearing calligraphy characters!  
  
BURN SITE  
[https://kenchiro.com/nft_data/wa_free/burn/](https://kenchiro.com/nft_data/wa_free/burn/)

There are no future price increases, roadmaps, or utilities.
